high_descs: Move right and then turn to your left twice so you are facing the counter to the right of the stone
Pick up a knife off of the counter
Use the knife to slice the tomato
Put the knife back down on to the counter
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter
Walk all the way to you left, and then turn left and walk to the fridge
Put the slice of tomato in the fridge and let it cool for a few seconds before pulling it out
Turn around and walk to the kitchen table
Put the slice of tomato down on the kitchen table
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato, chill it and put it on the kitchen table

high_descs: Go forward and turn to the left to face the apple on the counter.
Pick the knife up from the counter.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Put the knife on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Go to the left and face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the tomato in and then take it out and shut the door.
Turn around and face the white table.
Put the tomato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato on a table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Cut up the tomato on the counter.
Place the knife in front of the mug on the counter.
Pick up a piece of tomato.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Chill the piece of tomato in the fridge and then pick the piece of tomato up from the fridge and close the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the table across from the fridge.
Place the piece of tomato to the right of the paper towels.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled piece of tomato on the table across from the fridge.
